{"version":"1.2","person":{"datePublished":"2023-11-30","name":"Béatrix de Baffie","nameForms":[{"lang":"fr","fullText":"Béatrix de Baffie","parts":[{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Given","value":"Béatrix"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Surname","value":"de Baffie"}],"order":"EUROTYPIC"}],"gender":"Female","lifespan":"1210–1279","fullLifespan":"environ 1210–environ 1279","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/yzj6k/thumb200s.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"memoryArtifacts":[{"memoryType":"PHOTO","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7727-125007-33729-46/dist.png?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/171316898","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7727-125007-33729-46/thumb200s.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","deepZoomUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/deepzoomcloud/dzpatron/v1/TH-7727-125007-33729-46/scale?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","headline":"Baffie  D'or à trois molettes d'éperon de sable. ","@type":"ImageObject"}],"birthDate":"+1210","deathDate":"+1279","userCertifiedLifeSummary":" mariage avec  Agnon d' Olliergues\t\nMariage religieux :\tvers 1231\nSource : Collection inédite de chartes de franchises de Basse-Auvergne : XIIIe-XVe siècles - Marcellin Boudet - Bibliothèque Nationale de France page 62.\n\ndécès avant juillet 1249\nSource : Collection inédite de chartes de franchises de Basse-Auvergne : XIIIe-XVe siècles - Marcellin Boudet - Bibliothèque Nationale de France page 62.\nLa terre de Viverols, qui était une des quatre châtellenies du Livradois, avait pour vassaux : le Grand Prieur d’Auvergne, les seigneurs de Montravel, de Vertamy, de Fraissonnet, de Croz, de Montcelard, du Cluzet et du Chassaing.\n\nAu XIe siècle, Viverols appartenait aux de Baffie, vieille famille d’Auvergne, probablement originaire du Velay. Marcellin Boudet faisait descendre cette famille des SEMUR en Brionnais. Dalmas de Baffie possédait cette seigneurie en 1070.\n\nÉléonore de Baffie (1244-1285 ou après), dame du Livradois et d'Ambert, Riols et Marsac, Usson, Beauzac..., fille de Guillaume II le Vieux sire de Baffie et d’Eléonore du Forez, resta seule héritière de cette puissante maison à la mort de son frère Guillaume III de Baffie (vers 1273 ?) et de leur sœur Béatrix († 1249 ou avant).\nsource : Rhône médiéval\nrelevé 2023 JPR Teyssier Chalancon","events":[{"name":"Birth","sources":"0","year":"1210","date":"environ 1210"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1230","date":"1230","place":"Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France","age":"20","id":"G4TL-D9M"},{"name":"Marriage","sources":"0","year":"1235","date":"1235","place":"Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France","type":"Spousal","age":"25","id":"GSXY-Z8C"},{"name":"Death of Spouse","sources":"0","year":"1252","date":"octobre 1252","place":"Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne, France","age":"42","id":"GSXY-Z8C"},{"name":"Death of Child","sources":"0","year":"1272","date":"2 septembre 1272","place":"Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France","age":"62","id":"G4TL-D9M"},{"name":"Death","sources":"0","year":"1279","date":"environ 1279","age":"69"}],"spouse":[{"name":"Agne V d'Olliergues","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1180–1252","birthDate":"A+1180","deathDate":"+1252-10","age":72,"portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/b0k6k/thumb64.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"marriage":{"year":"1235","date":"1235","place":"Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France"},"@type":"Person","identifier":"GSXY-Z8C","url":"https://ancestors.familysearch.org/en/GSXY-Z8C/agne-v-d%27olliergues-1180-1252","published":true}],"children":[{"name":"Agnon VII d’Olliergues","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1230–1272","birthDate":"+1230","deathDate":"+1272-09-02","age":42,"portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/w5mpi/thumb64.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"othe